{"tid":903590,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"三人行必有豬隊友也","createTime":"2018-11-15T16:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T16:43:33.000Z","uid":141976,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"921aba0212ac5248f49db8d32473d1a1b39489f6","tid":903590,"uid":141976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:13:45.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇隔離Post,有唔少人話白衫醒目跑得快，因為深色衫拉住+卡位導致中間比車撞<br />\n<br />\n明明就見到係白衫拉佢出去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實喺深色衫食左死貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qA2pbmh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqA2pbmh.jpg&h=3fc55d1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始三個一齊過馬路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1prJrXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1prJrXg.jpg&h=c41d2cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哩個時間幾乎三個人同時發現左架車，白衫行最慢，剩低兩個平排<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jY6mdLn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjY6mdLn.jpg&h=c0d472b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哩個時侯2個都停低咗諗住退後，但喺身為賽跑冠軍嘅白衫快人一步，一支箭咁衝出去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h0NAidA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh0NAidA.png&h=97005f56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實白衫跑得快衝得過喺冇問題的<br />\n但佢做咗一個錯誤嘅決定，就喺拉埋隊友一齊衝<br />\n一啲默契都冇，隊友想退後，比佢監生拉咗出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ULMYfTM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FULMYfTM.jpg&h=3dc1dfb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哩張好清楚睇到架車係中間條線<br />\n如果佢唔係比人拉咗出去 根本就唔會有事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ijPyPee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FijPyPee.jpg&h=cd66a2cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mnGM9eq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmnGM9eq.png&h=5cde63da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇番上面4張圖<br />\n其實深色衫由頭到尾都冇郁過<br />\n唔知喺佢嚇到郁唔到<br />\n定喺因為佢同中間比白衫拉住<br />\n佢就咁企喺原地 冇中招<br />\n<br />\n中間同深衫原本企同一嗰位 就算企喺到唔郁 都唔會有事<br />\n<br />\n睇番時間 其實由發現到撞都喺1秒多少少嘅事 反應唔切好合理好正常 <br />\n<br />\n可惜佢地唔喺連燈仔 如果唔喺2秒入面應該可以跑番屋企再開埋Post用鍵盤建國"},{"pid":"ebd20376093dcdda3d76c079ca2cf27e336d68e6","tid":903590,"uid":141976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:24:36.000Z","msg":"圖3明顯見到中間想退後<br />\n<br />\n比隊友強行拖出去送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648978ef14a4996883ae7d7e33a59dd4e1fd095b","tid":903590,"uid":141976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:30:37.000Z","msg":"白衫拉完人出去跟住放手<br />\n<br />\n竟然仲有人話中間冇反應唔識退後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最快反應要避就係中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efaf395b1ee1aca2ee4210e06e2cc6b7e35e976","tid":903590,"uid":48358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:36:53.000Z","msg":"識唔識字"},{"pid":"a872708b70d2f90a212138441b5bf6771c40711b","tid":903590,"uid":141976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0efaf395b1ee1aca2ee4210e06e2cc6b7e35e976","tid":903590,"uid":48358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:36:53.000Z","msg":"識唔識字"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:43:33.000Z","msg":"邊度打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}